quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  43,36,Anyone disregards message de the Multus Gracious nos appoint devil est his constant companion
  43,37,Such companions divert them path factus them believe they guided
  43,38,When he advenit ante nos he dictus Oh Ego wish vos est prout far me prout 2 easts. Quod miserable companion
  43,39,It non console vos ut feria transgressors ut ambo vos share retribution
  43,40,Vos factus surdus hear vos factus blind vide those est far astray
  43,41,Nos let vos abiit it non nos surely requite them
  43,42,Nos show vos (retribution) nos promised them. Nos est foderator control them
  43,43,Vos steadfastly preach quod revealed vos; vos est rectus path
  43,44,Hoc est message vos tuus people totus de vos questioned
  43,45,Check messengers nos sent ante vos Habet nos ever appointed any alius deus! - beside the Multus Gracious - to worshipped